<title>
Transmission Warning Light Check
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition ON.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that transmission warning light (1) lights for about 2 sec. and then goes OFF. If anything faulty is found, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A5504016">Transmission Warning Light Does Not Come ON with Ignition ON and Engine Stopped (but Engine Can Be Started)</intxref>
 or 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A5504017">Transmission Warning Light Remains ON after Engine Starts</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
